{"type":"message","id":"ff4fb885","parentId":"3378ef37","timestamp":"2026-02-26T00:43:12.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"¡Hola! 👋  \nParece que acabas de despertar este espacio. ¿Quieres que nos presentemos? Puedo ayudarte a establecer tu identidad (nombre, estilo, emoji, etc.) y la tuya también.  \n\n¿Empezamos por mí o por ti?","textSignature":"msg_0e320834a05ea8c900699f971feb2c81a0b83b15d6ff15f3a0"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5-chat-latest","usage":{"input":10736,"output":58,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10794,"cost":{"input":0.013420000000000001,"output":0.00058,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014000000000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772066590203}}
