te equipo para OpenClaw (máquina personal compartida, servidor dedicado, etc.)?\n\nCon eso puedo alinear las protecciones, incluida la defensa contra prompt injection.","textSignature":"msg_0b054ca6540fefcb00699fa434767881a2a5529d386258adb4"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.1-codex","usage":{"input":2445,"output":553,"cacheRead":13184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16182,"cost":{"input":0.0030562500000000004,"output":0.00553,"cacheRead":0.001648,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01023425}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772069936534}}
{"type":"message","id":"a2129277","parentId":"32296c50","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:46:25.871Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Estoy usando linux en una maquina virtual dentro de mi iMac usando VMWare Fusion…me conecto directo con la interfaz de fusion…solo se accesa en mi red, no es publico… tengo snapshots…si el disco esta cifrado….si estan activas las updates… maquina personal compartida"}],"timestamp":1772070385864}}
{"type":"message","id":"eaf46152","parentId":"a2129277","timestamp":"2026-02-26T01:46:28.371Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Requesting read-only permissions**","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0b054ca6540fefcb00699fa5f3373081a2b80e8a8aaf887cd3\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpn6XzkiycgXrPr0lzkCd-5mK2UbM2YZe777XYwtD2thdRyfnFlBuk_aDktPW7Ec9V3BgfyA8roPWuPjbFoIHsagwZSeWGBzKlC09zFl_aHKrOx8pjDBghXG0HbeuPOOVYEM5WlxdkDoGSecDDpR8txm4VmHi6I8r7qY-aU2pQWJ1tYcTVPtqRci3K3KvDHQ3EEYilEOtjGkFHYut-FD6qWXl52b_uJFQ8qaug1itOk5LUE0OV4Mm8BAVqgXeWZ39_6zXSfhlDnKawMXbr9Y4sjZabMFqtaNaU4t-AUrSQqV7QprReWcHW5yXV4ZhfN8Dvj_8q5-AE7FRCNJ7ojZdAq5t_FA8cpumqr0iluRX_ZqCBUPhwl1ZiEeae3IPFY49S6gJM5fxYqPmfKPXd0kPFDrYeW2m1u2L9ZLrtS5K4CeuKLoFEglT6YaxSH53pltXA5o3ZlsTXOfx4rcbArSPUYDKrOpGkc7lHUahrQwE7MCsLBYdVyRyEY8suqcvWQy1xqbrc_jzvZR-DKocKr875jVNHub0IUKeqKvymvdDD6vAd8vpRNVPBdw7mqtlqvHEwRAsQK7U9mXwkV3j8oXSzdfeK18jRVN0gPAzi7VYYy6QQwIfVD0sHln4HLabbi6UPn0nyteY-y8Q9Q65vttjV8PoZh9vDqs5123JUEyqb-4KjoY9WbUQdzhCjBJoIGrDflozAYLWfw-sZ6PFC-ecYwEkxaMwLxyZDjvXAG2cU8taji9JN-MxLL-PFL_X-FxnwEqNQXWxQuooca7GAbH6fPrLkLQ-n4_9tUSVi6doYBlEEFLsD0bJql2GgIGAcBEjh97HQCnhhzNbLrtDXn_MEotdHm2sNQ_UblFVKkIh0oRU1pcU=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Requesting read-only permissions**\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]Perfecto, gracias por el contexto. ¿Autorizas entonces que ejecute las comprobaciones de solo lectura (sistema, puertos, firewall, `openclaw security audit --deep`, `openclaw update status`) para tener la línea base?","textSignature":"msg_0b054ca6540fefcb00699fa5f3c97481a2bf6c9b30bcd419dc"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.1-codex","usage":{"input":2957,"output":75,"cacheRead":12928,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15960,"cost":{"input":0.0036962500000000003,"output":0.00075,"cacheRead":0.001616,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006062250000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772070385869}}
