{"type":"message","id":"fd24b016","parentId":"7937a24c","timestamp":"2026-02-26T02:09:26.416Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Summarizing API key exposure and remediation steps**\n\nI’m putting together a summary about API key exposures found in .bash_history and Firefox cache. I’ll note the exposed key is nvapi, suggest verifying with vantage, and recommend cleaning the history and rotating the key as remediation steps. This will give the user clear next steps to secure the environment.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0b054ca6540fefcb00699fab53ea0c81a294290aa1ab1fa5a5\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpn6tVA3tqtSPXaS7xjx7VmFwH-7oahxdUVBAZE5MG8fC2gVIc5LSSE37zg8vLWXEym71y2MBYhN1ztQ4QLyWZjnO9t6VIuEfZqdleCw2-STnSb_pd_d0g5DMGsbZ-g1Sb5WBs3duqn_CJKqwcL_NxdtqDsWuwEWVZZ9s4Q9b5A_r7sJv89tZ0j3_hvGLGWW0_oxv2OWKv-tnAGHzYBsHo0zulXzrtJCqV-mMoJg6HOL29BlHNwjuNkv3pecoqcL2FuETLSk8fJQDyqYbdNsAqc2Cp-pgWwXWrkvv5JxKvZr8Ue7_awkfxdYTisQDNUdDtZx8HW9Cjvq4bEOc8MZPEjkCrWoqkTAQD04OnGeKbbABDgnV8aqhMEMiaHe3UbX9w2Sfr0iXP0l2DD8fikX4Ljwz2qmFw0lE7hgi_adqicjpqS6rIX8PpH-v6MMlZfAUjGZ1FuAMuTGzPZQbWky1pVRtGJkUcP7lRiSLumxGXCRiMgnF5S135eRl_sxbtLegrZjg-OG2hMR4iwsO3Af_ZEed7Exax2XxIKnLs34u-Cy7aZ7C4OiJn2KnGXFMsbPqtVCNRiyObeXfxhYHv2eyVc-rz4FSSkH1Wg_x-7epoXQ2rkAHHD8NvdoIx0qTXjJuqqshT3IsV-va5zkLDMfwSe-GvtAs10P1e40IRmSFRQD9l3A7FUs3NH-DxmXEgk-f-z-WdWD4KGM0kUupJGkk2CiH9-i8pelP2LX6X5_7aTDFxrPCYilkaklhiHd9v017ugsiFH31YjZetQoKYgyzw3Qmv-KIeDYUCwL_OQiLe8K8sQvHuxTUwurk7W2Er-lFBAVxzyDXL6VvjzOJ9yO8gBXu9ltRiMxEAVsAR7FR770PYxVUFpgyQ7HGavPebzUdPQKUEPEf8ZBemK0AEJaM_q0dToVwfVUDC6II_SWcWaHBycbFe7XC7wLLG5oqfnVOAV4RNH7kYAc96bkvvDawUO-X47lNx7n7dUqoizswjFBKNQVASw1Ucga9CjLyltPs6XUs3pOSPAaWUHbNzbb0h3WbZahqQcB3hLHGhm-fLzw3CTsBzcOWuP8gsw1-TdeAUDBEvQwTarL3gCOY047XCOHnz-gWIzadILqOQbnJg65IaAkFmjSry296Whrq7ev13J6gSXxlCDWKfwKEDnViUVL6VTDDhqeb4RHrM3Piq73iaZUPhtebo-WJgasxONT81IZxd29YswlGVaTGLq0NmOvjiyj8pXPKG2wV8JGwu3yNlpaR6SxesVa4ZGF7NoinECy8E8_CQzDgLaGoz__Ct5cHEtg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Summarizing API key exposure and remediation steps**\\n\\nI’m putting together a summary about API key exposures found in .bash_history and Firefox cache. I’ll note the exposed key is nvapi, suggest verifying with vantage, and recommend cleaning the history and rotating the key as remediation steps. This will give the user clear next steps to secure the environment.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]]Sí. Revisé el sistema en busca de cadenas `nvapi-…` y encontré la API key expuesta en tres lugares:\n\n1. **`~/.bash_history`** – hay varias entradas con `export NVIDIA_API_KEY=\"nvapi-Hyuwl…\"` y también un `openclaw config set …apiKey…` (líneas 33, 40, 42 y 43).  \n2. **Caché de Firefox / Outlook** – en `~/snap/firefox/common/.cache/mozilla/.../cache2/doomed/178145636` quedaron registros de un correo/copypaste que incluye la clave multiparámetro.  \n3. **(Relacionado) El historial del correo** indica que la clave se envió/pegó en un mensaje (`openclaw gateway config.patch … \"apiKey\": \"nvapi-Hyuwl…\"`). Aunque no tengo acceso directo al correo, la copia en caché confirma que ya quedó escrita en texto plano.\n\n➡️ **Recomendaciones inmediatas:**\n\n- **Rotar la API key en NVIDIA Dev** cuanto antes; asume que la clave actual está comprometida.  \n- **Limpiar los rastros locales**:\n  - Edita `~/.bash_history` (o bórralo completo) y vuelve a cargar la shell (`history -c && history -w`).  \n  - Elimina / purga la caché que contiene la clave:\n    ```bash\n    rm ~/.bash_history\n    rm -f ~/snap/firefox/common/.cache/mozilla/firefox/4230r6ea.default/cache2/doomed/178145636\n    ```\n    (Luego cierra Firefox para que no la reescriba.)  \n- **Evitar volver a escribir la clave** en texto plano. Mejor guárdala en un archivo `.env` con permisos 600 o usa un gestor de secretos y cárgala con `source`.\n\nDime si quieres que ejecute yo mismo la limpieza (borrado de historial y cachés) o prefieres hacerlo tú.","textSignature":"msg_0b054ca6540fefcb00699fab55d3b881a2a699b1252e7d0ada"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.1-codex","usage":{"input":720,"output":516,"cacheRead":100992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102228,"cost":{"input":0.0009000000000000001,"output":0.0051600000000000005,"cacheRead":0.012624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.018684}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772071756898}}
